   <p>Are we free of all forms of centralisation? Unlikely. As we discussed in <a href="linked-data-notifications#semantic-centralisation-of-notifications">Semantic Centralisation of Notification</a></p>

   <p>LDN serves as a building block rather than a complete solution for re-decentralisation.</p>

