What are the lessons learned? (specs is where it is at.. highly valuable but takes effort to align from a number of places.. social/technical challenges)
</section>

              "Third-party" publishers are not required. If anything, generally limits or has constraints on what and how Web resources can be published.

<p>Linked Research and dokieli is closely aligned with the original concept of <q cite="http://www.cs.cornell.edu/~ginsparg/physics/blurb/pg01unesco.html">self-archiving</q> - Ginsparg "school of thought", provided that anyone can share their Web resources from where they prefer.</p>
